  "title": "BUBBLE TEA BARISTA (ITEA)",
  "description": "<p><strong>iTea is a well-known local bubble tea chain in Singapore, iTea focuses on offering good-quality drinks at neighbourhood-friendly prices. More than 50 outlets in Singapore and we are expanding to more outlets in Singapore.</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>Customer service:</strong> Greet customers, take orders accurately, and provide friendly, prompt service.</li>\n  <li><strong>Beverage preparation:</strong> Prepare milk teas and other drinks according to company recipes and quality standards. This includes cooking tapioca pearls and preparing other toppings and ingredients.</li>\n  <li><strong>Cashiering:</strong> Handle transactions, collect payments, and process orders at the point of sale.</li>\n  <li><strong>Store operations:</strong> Assist with daily store operations, including opening and closing duties, and may include handling delivery orders.</li>\n  <li><strong>Cleanliness and organization:</strong> Maintain a clean, safe, and organized work environment by cleaning equipment, workstations, and the overall store.</li>\n  <li><strong>Inventory and stocking:</strong> Monitor stock levels, restock supplies as needed, and assist with inventory management and stocktaking.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Strong customer service skills.</li>\n  <li>Ability to work in a fast-paced environment.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Benefits:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Full timers (Up to $3000 Gross salary) (5 days 44 hours per week)</li>\n  <li>Part timer ($11.30/hour - $12.30/hour) (Flexible working hours (For Part Timer)</li>\n  <li>Training will be provided + Career advancement</li>\n  <li>Yearly increment &amp; AWS</li>\n  <li>Productivity allowance and other incentives</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>",
